# coffee-jasmine-code-coverage-example

A quick example on how to do code coverage with the following tools:

- CoffeeScript
- Jasmine
- Istanbul
- Grunt

## How to run

First, install grunt-cli globally:

```
npm install -g grunt
```

Next, install all required packages:

```
npm install
```

And finally, run grunt with one of the following commands:

```
grunt
grunt test
grunt watch:coffee
grunt watch:spec
grunt deploy
```